data.description:
This lovely Key West Style Home is graced with eye catching curb appeal. Entering the home you are immediately drawn to the warmth and attention to details.The first stunning feature is the Heart Pine wide plank flooring throughout the home. The abundance of windows allow natural lighting. The living area features a vaulted wall, natural wood ceiling detail and a cozy gas fireplace with a very unique distressed wood mantle.  Perfectly situated to increase your living space is the easily accessed porch room with an outdoor fireplace, TV, and furnishings that invite you and your guests to totally relax while enjoying the water views and natural habitat. An attached open deck is perfect for soakng up the beautiful SC sunshine.A powder room is conveniently located in the foyer Just off the living area is a room perfect for gaming, crafting or an impromptu lunch and then ..... a dream kitchen with an outstanding island with  gorgeous wood overlay for dining and serving a crowd. Equipped with a beverage fridge, microwave, storage and a breath taking linear chandelier. The chef's kitchen  features a gas stove, granite counters, subway tile backsplash, stainless appliances, floor to ceiling cabinetry and lovely windows for enjoying the water and bridge views.Sliders open to a deck for grilling or enjoying your morning coffee. 2 spacious guest bedrooms share a lovely bathroom on the first floor. The master ensuite is located upstairs and features nice ceiling detail with access to a private porch for peaceful relaxation. The bath is just perfect with a privacy water closet, steam shower, Jacuzzi Tub, dressing table, vanity and a tremendous walk-in closet. A soundproof office/media room or a could be guest sleepover room completes the upstairs layout. 
Underneath, the home offers two bay parking garage, a storage room, an outfitted bedroom with sitting area for overflow guests.
An outdoor shower is ideal after a day on the beach. The yard is fenced and the property sits next door to a preserved area assuring privacy and unobstructed Harbor Island Views.
The home is situated to enjoy the common area with picnic tables for hosting large gatherings under the shade of awesome oak trees.
 The metal roofing, Bahama Shutters, Key West Design and attention to detail make this house very special. The owners have maintained the property to a high standard with HVAC and hot water heater in 2022, blown foam insulation and incorporated high end details throughout the home. 
Harbour Key is a short distance to the island amenities which include the 2.5 mile natural beach, crabbing/fishing decks, tennis/basket/pickle ball courts, fitness, gym and the community pools.
The lovely furnishings convey with the home.....making it move in ready to begin island living at it's best!
